to how much he loves you.

259
00:22:39.691 --> 00:22:42.027
Is the crew
from the other van already armed?

260
00:22:42.527 --> 00:22:45.238
All set. One. two. three. four. five. six.

261
00:22:52.621 --> 00:22:53.955
