Poe. what's wrong?

400
00:34:23.936 --> 00:34:28.900
My dad gets up at 4:30.
and I have 15 minutes to get home. so…

401
00:34:28.983 --> 00:34:30.777
<i>♪ I always let the good ones go ♪</i>

402
